(1, 'eli@taylormadetraffic.com', 'df749b0c433f2d82151488ab8861c200', 'Eli A. Taylor', 'E.A.Taylor', 10, 1389581389, 1389581386, '<p>Below are a few of the projects I''ve built over the past decade. My role and the <a href=''/team''>team members</a> whom I can remember are tagged along with the <a href=''/technologies''>technologies</a> that were used. If you have a project in mind and want to find my similar experiences than filter by clicking the tags.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am currently focused on building mobile applications around music, art, and education. However, even in developing the driest of subjects - automated healthcare advertising - I''ve found fun in problem solving and strategy.\r\n\r\n\r\nI have developed for all ends of the stack, but my strongest expertise is in desktop-style interface engineering, such as browser plugins, heavy-ajax sites, and mobile applications.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I''m always available via email: <span class=''alink''>eat@taylormadetraffic.com</span></p>', 'http://www.facebook.com/MrEliATaylor', 'http://co.linkedin.com/in/elitaylor', NULL);
